INSERT INTO "Event" VALUES ('cmnz71rs600fkxphpyrdcdu2w', 'Thirty Seconds to Mars Presents A Beautiful Lie vs This Is War', 'CONCERT', 'Thirty Seconds To Mars', '3Arena', 'Dublin', 'IE', '2027-05-01 00:00:00', NULL, 'https://www.ticketmaster.ie/thirty-seconds-to-mars-presents-a-dublin-01-05-2027/event/18006487B617DF14', NULL, 'Information on VIP Packages: All VIP attendees must be at least 18 years of age to participate without a parent, legal guardian, or designated adult chaperone. Guests under the age of 18 will not be permitted to attend VIP activities unless accompanied by an adult aged 18 or older. Additionally, any guest under the age of 18 must be accompanied by their parent, legal guardian, or adult chaperone in the official photo opportunity with the band. Side stage viewing is an immersive experience that offers a rare perspective of the show from a designated standing area near the stage. Location will vary by venue. For accessibility info please email info@adventuresinwonderland.com Check-in time and location will be emailed out by Adventures In Wonderland 3-5 days prior to the day of the show. Please check your spam folder! This information will also be posted on thirtysecondstomars.com prior to the show. Your ticket will be given to you at VIP check-in. All sales are final.', 'https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/a/a02/a6886ca9-b28a-4d84-b59c-adfde59c7a02_RETINA_LANDSCAPE_16_9.jpg', 'Rock', 'TICKETMASTER', '1AbZk36GkeUAWHf', 'tm-thirty-seconds-to-mars-3arena-dublin-2027-05-01', 53.347512, -6.228482, true, '2026-04-14 22:29:19.974', '2026-04-14 22:29:19.974', NULL, NULL, NULL, '18:30:00', 'Pop', false, 'https://www.facebook.com/thirtysecondstomars', 'https://instagram.com/30secondstomars/', 'https://open.spotify.com/artist/0RqtSIYZmd4fiBKVFqyIqD', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/30SECONDSTOMARS', 'http://www.thirtysecondstomars.com/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/30secondstomars', false, false);
